# Management Summary & Insights

## Key Findings
- Certain departments consistently exceeded budget limits, indicating the need for improved cost controls
- KPI scores showed correlation with expense management efficiency
- Departments with controlled spending demonstrated stronger performance metrics

## Recommendations
- Implement tighter budget monitoring processes
- Introduce monthly variance review meetings
- Use KPI dashboards for proactive decision-making

## Business Impact
- Improved financial transparency
- Better cost control
- Enhanced operational efficiency
